        <p><strong>The Gambia</strong>, the smallest mainland country in Africa, is a hidden gem waiting to be
            discovered.
            With its stunning beaches, vibrant culture, and welcoming people, it has earned the title of the 'Smiling
            Coast
            of Africa'. This guide provides you with all the necessary information to ensure a memorable and
            trouble-free
            journey in this West African haven.</p>
